  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div xml:id="Aink401-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">
            kaṭimaṉaic ceṉṟuvanta cevili uvanta uḷḷattaḷāy naṟṟāykkuc colliyatu.
          </p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            The foster-mother who has gone and returned from their home speaking rejoicefully to the 'real' mother. 
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Aink401">
            <lg type="edition">
             <l> maṟiyiṭaip paṭutta māṉpiṇai pōlap</l>
             <l> putalva ṉaṭuvaṇa ṉāka naṉṟu</l>     
             <l>miṉitu maṉṟavavar kiṭakkai muṉiviṉṟi</l>             
<l>              nīṉiṟa viyalakaṅ kavaiiya         </l>
<l>              vīṉu mumparum peṟalaruṅ kuraittē.</l>
            </lg>
            <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            It was certainly good and sweet, them lying down without affliction, the[ir] son between [them] like a stag and doe with [their] calf between them - it is something difficult to obtain both in this world which the vast blue expanse embraces and in the beyond. 
            </p>
        </div>
    </body>
